title: The Fog is here
description: We've received our first victim reports, the tsunami is here What this means if you are a student: Sh1mmer is obselete No good way to unenroll anymore Proxies are back in fashion I guess What this means if you are a sysadmin Any replacements which you RMA shim after (screen replacements and such) won't work unless you know some way around it (contact Google about shimless RMA possibly?) Pretty much any RMA shim based repair tools are useless now It was nice knowing y'all while the bug lasted, good day Slight description: the tsunami makes it impossible to disable WP on CR50 Chromebooks, without the Google auth thingy that only very special ppl have
